## Per-Token Contracts (Deployed by Factory)

Each call to `TokenFactory.createTokenLaunch(name, symbol)` deploys a full suite of contracts:

| Contract | Role |
|---|---|
| `PumpToken` | ERC20 token with controlled mint/burn |
| `BondingCurveSale` | Handles buy/sell during bonding curve phase |
| `VestingVault` | Locks tokens and enforces market-driven unlocks |
| `MarketHealthOracle` | Computes health score from on-chain signals |
| `LiquidityBootstrapper` | Seeds DEX liquidity when curve completes |

Contract addresses are emitted in the `TokenLaunched` event from the TokenFactory transaction.

---

## Verification

Contracts compiled with Solidity `0.8.30+commit.73712a01`, optimizer enabled (200 runs).
